wifi adapter commands
apt install dkms git
apt install build-essential libelf-dev linux-headers-$(uname -r)
apt install build-essential libelf-dev linux-headers-$(uname -r) --fix-broken
apt install build-essential libelf-dev linux-headers-$(uname -r) --fix-missing
apt install realtek-rtl88xxau-dkms
apt install build-essential libelf-dev linux-headers-$(uname -r)
apt install build-essential libelf-dev linux-headers-$(uname -r) --fix-missing
apt install build-essential libelf-dev linux-headers-$(uname -r) --fix-broken

if by any chance these commands are not working at first time then repeat all these commands 2-3 times wifi driver will definitely installed.
